      {
        "id": 2470526,
        "name": "Brian Buzzini",
        "username": "B_Buzzini",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/b_buzzini/{size}/636_2.png",
        "created_at": "2018-08-23T23:15:15.000Z",
        "cooked": "<ul>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/note.asp?iWine=837670&amp;iNote=7198612\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><strong>1993 Domaine Bertheau (Pierre et Fran\u00e7ois) Chambolle-Musigny</strong></a> <em>- France, Burgundy, C\u00f4te de Nuits, Chambolle-Musigny (8/23/2018)</em><br>\nOne of the most satisfying purchases I\u2019ve even made! Bought a bunch of these about 4yrs ago, and I think this is the 5th bottle\u2026ALL have been well above expectations! This one had tons of mold under capsule\u2026corked pulled out nice and spongy, yet firm. Smelled the cork\u2026and damn\u2026it smelled of oxidized wine? Quickly smelled into the bottle, and it smelled of beautiful cherries! Ahhhh\u2026another fantastic bottle! And it is! Wonderful mix of sous bois and bright/tart cherries, pretty strawberry field nose, more old leather than I\u2019ve encountered before, slight menthol. This bottle not as silky smooth as others\u2026little more astringent, tart edges\u2026yet still quite smooth and round, with a good kick of sour cherry skin acidity and crushed geology. LOVE the red fruits\u2026the pretty feminine perfume florals\u2026tons of complexity for a village effort. The astringency kicks it down a couple notches\u2026but I\u2019ve only had it open in bottle for an hour, so will report back it some airtime integrates. Super stuff! Would love to try an Amoureuses in this vintage! <em><strong>(93 pts.)</strong></em>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Posted from <a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">CellarTracker</a></em></p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/original/3X/1/3/1328e158bc814efa6b57f03ab88bdd86a0cf8564.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/1328e158bc814efa6b57f03ab88bdd86a0cf8564\" title=\"\"><img src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/1/3/1328e158bc814efa6b57f03ab88bdd86a0